research/history/memory.json:919:      "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 由轻量 router 选出单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。在线侧可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“router 选静态子库 + 子库内查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r51 仅把 NUM_EXPERTS 从 16 提到 32，在保持 ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk、K=192、EF=1、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 不变时，如果当前低成本带里纯 MoE-like routed sublibrary 仍有未吃满的静态容量收益，那么不带 trunk 的更大 expert 总容量应在仍可接受的 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并回答 routed-only 方向是否值得继续作为独立低成本前沿推进。",
research/history/memory.json:922:      "family_name": "expert_topk",
research/history/memory.json:928:      "architecture": "expert_topk",
research/history/memory.json:937:      "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 由轻量 router 选出单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。在线侧可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“router 选静态子库 + 子库内查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r68 仅把 K 从 192 降到 160，在保持 ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk、NUM_EXPERTS=32、EF=1、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 不变时，如果 r68 的收益来自 routed-only MoE-like 子库容量确实更匹配当前 target，而不只是依赖较大的查表预算，那么该 family 应能在更低 total_cost 下保留大部分质量，从而把这条直接兼容的 routed-only 前沿向左延伸。",
research/history/memory.json:940:      "family_name": "expert_topk",
research/history/memory.json:946:      "architecture": "expert_topk",
research/history/memory.json:955:      "hypothesis": "Final reconstruction stays x_hat = sum_{r=1..R} beta_r(x) u_r + sum_{i in S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} alpha_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}, with t(x) = sum_{r=1..R} beta_r(x) u_r. This exports to the LUTurbo/Lottable path as a static trunk table lookup plus a single routed static expert sublibrary lookup plus a finite weighted sum, so `lowrank_expert_topk` is extended-compatible. Compatibility screen before proposing this round: `expert_topk` is directly compatible; `lowrank_expert_topk`, `lowrank_expert_residual`, and `two_stage_residual_expert` are extended-compatible; batch-coupled families such as `batch_topk` and `adaptive_budget_topk` are incompatible and must stay off the active frontier. Relative to r60, changing only `TRUNK_RANK` from 64 to 32 tests the missing mid-trunk point in the low-cost band: if the routed-only improvement from r59 to r60 was not all-or-nothing, this should recover much of r60's FVU while moving left from the current lowrank+expert anchor and potentially create a new compatible Pareto segment between `expert_topk` and `lowrank_expert_residual`.",
research/history/memory.json:958:      "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/memory.json:964:      "architecture": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/memory.json:973:      "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的链路是：先做共享低维投影 h(x)，再做 router 选单个静态 expert 子库，再由该 expert 的小型 head 在低维空间上打分并做 local top-k，最后把 (e,i) 扁平化为静态库查表上的有限加权和；静态库本身不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容。兼容性先验在本轮保持清晰：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 与本轮新增的 `factorized_expert_topk` 都属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，只能留作历史参考，不能继续驱动 frontier。相对 r69 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`EF=1` 与训练 recipe 不变，直接回答当前高优先级问题：把 shared low-rank basis 放进 expert 内部 head，而不是放在 expert 外部做全局 trunk，是否能在不拉长 active path 的前提下形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。按当前 proxy 粗估，shared basis + active expert head 的 encoder 成本应仍落在约 0.3x 量级，配合 `K=160` 的部署成本后总成本预计仍在约 0.45x-0.5x 带，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。",
