的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4714:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1217:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1161:research/history/logs/agent_round_0040_repair_1.stdout.log:6032:    "summary": "\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u4e0a\u505a\u7b2c\u4e09\u4e2a\u90bb\u57df\u626b\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8fdb\u5165\u4e0b\u4e00\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff1a\u5b9e\u73b0\u6700\u5c0f\u53ef\u8fd0\u884c\u7684 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u539f\u578b\u3002\u4ee5 r27 \u7684 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` \u4e3a matched baseline\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff0c\u5148\u9a8c\u8bc1\u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f\u7ed3\u6784\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4715:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1221:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1181:research/history/logs/agent_action_0035.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择一个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设：在 EF=1、K=128 的低开销带，lowrank trunk 先吸收平滑主干、expert local top-k 再处理残差，能比 plain expert_topk 与同带宽 plain selector 提供更好的 FVU/total_cost 权衡，并形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 r12->lowrank_expert_topk(K=128) 给出有效信号且 FVU 明显优于当前 0.38x-0.56x 邻域锚点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 K 到 160，验证该 family 在 0.69x total_cost 处是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果该原型训练不稳或收益不足，则优先继续实现 `lowrank + expert + residual`，而不是回到 plain topk/jumprelu 的局部扫点。"],"notes_to_memory":["已按 sae-architecture-integration checklist 完成新 family 接线：`lowrank_expert_topk` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","新增原型 family 的导出形式为 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 静态库约束，兼容性应视为扩展兼容。","已完成 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`lowrank_expert_topk`, K=128, EF=1 通过。","当前原型采用固定 4 experts、active_experts=1、无新增 tunable 参数，因此本轮只需改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。","在 target proxy(1024x4096) 上，`lowrank_expert_topk` 的估算成本为：K=128 -> total 0.56x；K=160 -> total 0.69x；K=192 -> total 0.81x。低开销起点应优先从 K=128 开始。"],"reference_round":12,"self_review":"这轮只改了一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`，相对 r12 保持 K=128、EF=1、LR=8e-4、optimizer=adam 不变，归因清晰。代码侧只做最小 family 原型接线，没有引入新 tunable，因此不存在 override/runner 静默回退风险。风险是当前 prototype 的 expert 数和 active_experts 仍是固定值，若首轮效果一般，不能立刻下结论否定 `lowrank + expert` 方向本身。","summary":"已实现并 smoke 通过新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` family，用最小 lowrank+expert 原型覆盖当前高优先级未验证结构槽位。建议下一轮以 r12(topk K=128 EF=1) 为参考，只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，先在约 0.56x total_cost 的低开销带验证该 family 是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4716:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1224:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1210:research/history/logs/agent_round_0036.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":35,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。相对 r35 仅改 K: 128 -> 160，回答一个结构问题：在 lowrank+expert 这个新 family 中，适度增加 sparse residual 容量后，FVU 是否会比 plain expert_topk 的同成本邻域下降更快，从而证明 trunk+expert 组合值得继续推进。","summary":"继续验证新 family `lowrank_expert_topk`，不回到 old-family 微调。以 r35 为参考只提高 `K` 到 160，在仍低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x 总成本的前提下，检查 lowrank trunk + local expert residual 是否开始形成比 `expert_topk` 更有竞争力的中低成本 Pareto 斜率。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r35 仅修改 `K`。这是对刚引入的新结构做最小必要的第二个锚点，而不是回到 plain selector 的局部扫点。按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 的 total_cost 约 0.69x，仍在预算内，且能直接回答该 family 是否具有继续扩展价值。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk K=160` 相对 r35 出现清晰 FVU 改善且斜率优于 `expert_topk`，下一轮仍保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 到 192，确认该 family 在 0.8x 附近是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果 `K=160` 仍无明显收益，则应停止继续打磨该两段式原型，优先转向 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`，而不是退回 plain `topk/jumprelu/factorized_topk`。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","当前已完成新 family 首轮验证；Round 36 只补第二个 K 锚点，目标是判断 lowrank+expert 的 FVU-cost 斜率，而不是刷新全局最低 FVU。","成本估算：`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 约为 total 0.69x（selection 0.22x + deployment 0.47x），显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x。","若该点仍弱，应把后续结构预算转向三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`。"],"touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4717:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1225:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1216:research/history/logs/agent_round_0036.stdout.log:391:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":35,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。相对 r35 仅改 K: 128 -> 160，回答一个结构问题：在 lowrank+expert 这个新 family 中，适度增加 sparse residual 容量后，FVU 是否会比 plain expert_topk 的同成本邻域下降更快，从而证明 trunk+expert 组合值得继续推进。","summary":"继续验证新 family `lowrank_expert_topk`，不回到 old-family 微调。以 r35 为参考只提高 `K` 到 160，在仍低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x 总成本的前提下，检查 lowrank trunk + local expert residual 是否开始形成比 `expert_topk` 更有竞争力的中低成本 Pareto 斜率。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r35 仅修改 `K`。这是对刚引入的新结构做最小必要的第二个锚点，而不是回到 plain selector 的局部扫点。按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 的 total_cost 约 0.69x，仍在预算内，且能直接回答该 family 是否具有继续扩展价值。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk K=160` 相对 r35 出现清晰 FVU 改善且斜率优于 `expert_topk`，下一轮仍保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 到 192，确认该 family 在 0.8x 附近是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果 `K=160` 仍无明显收益，则应停止继续打磨该两段式原型，优先转向 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`，而不是退回 plain `topk/jumprelu/factorized_topk`。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","当前已完成新 family 首轮验证；Round 36 只补第二个 K 锚点，目标是判断 lowrank+expert 的 FVU-cost 斜率，而不是刷新全局最低 FVU。","成本估算：`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 约为 total 0.69x（selection 0.22x + deployment 0.47x），显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x。","若该点仍弱，应把后续结构预算转向三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`。"],"touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4718:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1228:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1233:research/history/logs/agent_round_0037_repair_1.stdout.log:43:    "summary": "不继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做第三个邻域扫点，而是进入下一结构槽位：实现最小可运行的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 原型。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证三段式结构本身是否值得继续。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4719:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1229:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1234:research/history/logs/agent_round_0037_repair_1.stdout.log:57:    "description": "不继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做第三个邻域扫点，而是进入下一结构槽位：实现最小可运行的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 原型。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证三段式结构本身是否值得继续。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4720:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1249:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1357:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选单个 expert 子库 e(x)，并在该子库内做局部 top-k，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线。我将 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容。r42 已在默认 trunk_rank=384、K=192、EF=1 下得到 val_FVU≈0.0888，但总成本约 0.81x；主假设是把 `TRUNK_RANK` 单独降到 128 后，可把总成本压到约 0.44x，同时保留足够多的质量，从而在 <0.5x 带形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。由于这是该 family 首次把 `TRUNK_RANK` 接入 AutoResearch override 链路，本轮首先是参数生效确认轮，结果只有在 round*.config.json 与 checkpoint config.json 都出现 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 后才可作为结构证据。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 生效且 FVU 仍明显优于当前 <0.5x anchor，则下一轮继续同 family，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=64`，测试 lowrank+expert 是否还能再向更低成本延伸。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的质量退化过大，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=192`，寻找低成本与质量之间的折中点。","如果参数未真正进入训练配置或 checkpoint，则下一轮继续做接线修复，不对该 family 的质量做结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 现已接入 `TRUNK_RANK` override 白名单；`validate_env_overrides` 对 `(ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, TRUNK_RANK=128)` 已通过。","兼容性注册表已补入 `lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`，三者均按 LUTurbo 导出约束标记为扩展兼容，避免新结构结果继续被 compatible frontier/prompt 过滤掉。","基于当前实现的成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x，明显低于 r42 默认 trunk 的约 0.81x。"],"reference_round":42,"self_review":"本轮代码改动只做运行时 unblock：一是给 `lowrank_expert_topk` 打通 `TRUNK_RANK` override 白名单，二是把当前已实现的 expert/lowrank family 明确登记为扩展兼容。真正训练配置相对 r42 仍只改 1 个 env 参数：`TRUNK_RANK=128`。这满足单变量原则，也符合“先消除运行时/观测 blocker，再做结构判断”的优先级。风险在于本轮仍是首个接线验证轮，若只看到训练结果而不检查 round config/checkpoint config，就可能把无效 override 误判成结构结论。","summary":"先修复两个当前 blocker：`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `TRUNK_RANK` override 接线，以及 lowrank+expert 系列在兼容性注册表中的缺失标注。随后基于 r42 只下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 128，做一个低成本验证轮，优先回答这条 lowrank+expert 结构能否把约 0.81x 的质量点压进 <0.5x 成本带。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4721:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1278:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1444:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2198:research/history/timeline.jsonl:135:{"event_id": "evt_1774725657997038484", "ts": 1774725657, "event": "training_started", "round": 42, "session_id": "019d3598-4bd0-7eb0-b116-6005526ca7d8", "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"run_name": "round0042_standard_1774725657", "config": {"architecture": "lowrank_expert_topk", "expansion_factor": 1, "k": 192, "optimizer": "adam", "lr": "8e-4", "hookpoints": "layers.[3].self_attn.q_proj", "batch_size": 1, "grad_acc_steps": 8, "micro_acc_steps": 1, "auxk_alpha": 0.03125, "dead_feature_threshold": 10000000, "use_hadamard": false, "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "target_profile": {"profile_id": "qwen3_0p6b_layer3_q_proj_fused_qkv_proxy_v1", "training_hookpoint": "layers.[3].self_attn.q_proj", "d_in": 1024, "n_output": 4096, "elbow_threshold_path": "thresholds/Qwen3-0.6B/thresholds_q.json", "cost_model_label": "train on q_proj activations; cost proxy uses fused QKV deployment matrix 1024x4096", "original_matmul_accesses": 4194304}, "cost_model_label": "train on q_proj activations; cost proxy uses fused QKV deployment matrix 1024x4096", "d_in": 1024, "n_output": 4096, "original_matmul_accesses": 4194304, "factorized_hidden_dim": 256}}}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4722:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1281:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1450:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2224:research/history/logs/agent_action_0036.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":35,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。相对 r35 仅改 K: 128 -> 160，回答一个结构问题：在 lowrank+expert 这个新 family 中，适度增加 sparse residual 容量后，FVU 是否会比 plain expert_topk 的同成本邻域下降更快，从而证明 trunk+expert 组合值得继续推进。","summary":"继续验证新 family `lowrank_expert_topk`，不回到 old-family 微调。以 r35 为参考只提高 `K` 到 160，在仍低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x 总成本的前提下，检查 lowrank trunk + local expert residual 是否开始形成比 `expert_topk` 更有竞争力的中低成本 Pareto 斜率。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r35 仅修改 `K`。这是对刚引入的新结构做最小必要的第二个锚点，而不是回到 plain selector 的局部扫点。按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 的 total_cost 约 0.69x，仍在预算内，且能直接回答该 family 是否具有继续扩展价值。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk K=160` 相对 r35 出现清晰 FVU 改善且斜率优于 `expert_topk`，下一轮仍保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 到 192，确认该 family 在 0.8x 附近是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果 `K=160` 仍无明显收益，则应停止继续打磨该两段式原型，优先转向 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`，而不是退回 plain `topk/jumprelu/factorized_topk`。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","当前已完成新 family 首轮验证；Round 36 只补第二个 K 锚点，目标是判断 lowrank+expert 的 FVU-cost 斜率，而不是刷新全局最低 FVU。","成本估算：`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 约为 total 0.69x（selection 0.22x + deployment 0.47x），显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x。","若该点仍弱，应把后续结构预算转向三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`。"],"touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4723:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1282:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1453:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2227:research/history/logs/agent_action_0037.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在与 r27 相同的 EF=1、K=192 recipe 下，把 `expert_topk` 升级为 `lowrank + expert + residual` 三段式结构，能回答‘仅有 lowrank+expert 仍不足时，加入第二段 residual 修正是否会形成新的结构性 Pareto 段’这个当前更关键的问题。","summary":"不继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做第三个邻域扫点，而是进入下一结构槽位：实现最小可运行的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 原型。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证三段式结构本身是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：运行配置相对 r27 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮优先解决结构未知量，而不是继续在已显示弱势的 recipe 上局部打磨。选择 r27 而不是 r34/r18，是因为它提供了与 expert 路由最接近的 matched baseline，同时避免把结论混入 jumprelu 或大 K 主线。风险是该三段式原型在 K=192 处总成本大概率落在中成本带而非极低成本带，但这仍符合当前阶段允许用少量中成本质量锚点回答结构问题的策略。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_residual` 首轮能稳定训练且 FVU 明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配是否是主要控制旋钮。","如果该 family 训练稳定但收益有限，下一轮优先只改 `TRUNK_RANK`，验证 trunk 是否过重并侵蚀了低成本收益。","如果三段式 family 连 matched baseline 都无法明显改善，应停止继续围绕该原型打磨，转向 `two-stage residual expert` 方向，而不是回到 plain selector 家族。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","本轮要回答的是三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4724:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1283:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1455:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2231:research/history/logs/agent_round_0035.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择一个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设：在 EF=1、K=128 的低开销带，lowrank trunk 先吸收平滑主干、expert local top-k 再处理残差，能比 plain expert_topk 与同带宽 plain selector 提供更好的 FVU/total_cost 权衡，并形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 r12->lowrank_expert_topk(K=128) 给出有效信号且 FVU 明显优于当前 0.38x-0.56x 邻域锚点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 K 到 160，验证该 family 在 0.69x total_cost 处是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果该原型训练不稳或收益不足，则优先继续实现 `lowrank + expert + residual`，而不是回到 plain topk/jumprelu 的局部扫点。"],"notes_to_memory":["已按 sae-architecture-integration checklist 完成新 family 接线：`lowrank_expert_topk` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","新增原型 family 的导出形式为 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 静态库约束，兼容性应视为扩展兼容。","已完成 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`lowrank_expert_topk`, K=128, EF=1 通过。","当前原型采用固定 4 experts、active_experts=1、无新增 tunable 参数，因此本轮只需改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。","在 target proxy(1024x4096) 上，`lowrank_expert_topk` 的估算成本为：K=128 -> total 0.56x；K=160 -> total 0.69x；K=192 -> total 0.81x。低开销起点应优先从 K=128 开始。"],"reference_round":12,"self_review":"这轮只改了一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`，相对 r12 保持 K=128、EF=1、LR=8e-4、optimizer=adam 不变，归因清晰。代码侧只做最小 family 原型接线，没有引入新 tunable，因此不存在 override/runner 静默回退风险。风险是当前 prototype 的 expert 数和 active_experts 仍是固定值，若首轮效果一般，不能立刻下结论否定 `lowrank + expert` 方向本身。","summary":"已实现并 smoke 通过新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` family，用最小 lowrank+expert 原型覆盖当前高优先级未验证结构槽位。建议下一轮以 r12(topk K=128 EF=1) 为参考，只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，先在约 0.56x total_cost 的低开销带验证该 family 是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
