是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4767:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1538:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:927:research/history/logs/agent_round_0040_repair_1.stdout.log:6032:    "summary": "\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u4e0a\u505a\u7b2c\u4e09\u4e2a\u90bb\u57df\u626b\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8fdb\u5165\u4e0b\u4e00\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff1a\u5b9e\u73b0\u6700\u5c0f\u53ef\u8fd0\u884c\u7684 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u539f\u578b\u3002\u4ee5 r27 \u7684 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` \u4e3a matched baseline\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff0c\u5148\u9a8c\u8bc1\u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f\u7ed3\u6784\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4768:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1544:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:937:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:3:  "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 修正；因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路。兼容性判断：`lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容。主假设是：相对 r27 的纯 `expert_topk`，加入轻量 low-rank trunk 后，能显著改善重构质量，并回答 `lowrank + expert` 这条高优先级结构线是否值得继续，即使首点落在中成本带也有信息价值。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4769:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1545:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:938:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:4:  "summary": "不回到 plain selector 邻域微调，也不继续对未知结果的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 做预设调参。本轮以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，先拿到 `lowrank + expert` 这条结构线在当前 target 上的首个真实训练点。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4770:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1549:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:942:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:24:    "如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 首点明显优于 r27 `expert_topk`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK` 向低成本方向压缩，测试是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4771:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1552:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:946:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:419:  "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 修正；因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路。兼容性判断：`lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容。主假设是：相对 r27 的纯 `expert_topk`，加入轻量 low-rank trunk 后，能显著改善重构质量，并回答 `lowrank + expert` 这条高优先级结构线是否值得继续，即使首点落在中成本带也有信息价值。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4772:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1553:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:947:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:420:  "summary": "不回到 plain selector 邻域微调，也不继续对未知结果的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 做预设调参。本轮以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，先拿到 `lowrank + expert` 这条结构线在当前 target 上的首个真实训练点。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4773:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1557:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:951:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:440:    "如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 首点明显优于 r27 `expert_topk`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK` 向低成本方向压缩，测试是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0051.stdout.log:4774:research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1560:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:954:research/history/logs/agent_round_0035.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择一个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设：在 EF=1、K=128 的低开销带，lowrank trunk 先吸收平滑主干、expert local top-k 再处理残差，能比 plain expert_topk 与同带宽 plain selector 提供更好的 FVU/total_cost 权衡，并形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 r12->lowrank_expert_topk(K=128) 给出有效信号且 FVU 明显优于当前 0.38x-0.56x 邻域锚点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 K 到 160，验证该 family 在 0.69x total_cost 处是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果该原型训练不稳或收益不足，则优先继续实现 `lowrank + expert + residual`，而不是回到 plain topk/jumprelu 的局部扫点。"],"notes_to_memory":["已按 sae-architecture-integration checklist 完成新 family 接线：`lowrank_expert_topk` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","新增原型 family 的导出形式为 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 静态库约束，兼容性应视为扩展兼容。","已完成 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`lowrank_expert_topk`, K=128, EF=1 通过。","当前原型采用固定 4 experts、active_experts=1、无新增 tunable 参数，因此本轮只需改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。","在 target proxy(1024x4096) 上，`lowrank_expert_topk` 的估算成本为：K=128 -> total 0.56x；K=160 -> total 0.69x；K=192 -> total 0.81x。低开销起点应优先从 K=128 开始。"],"reference_round":12,"self_review":"这轮只改了一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`，相对 r12 保持 K=128、EF=1、LR=8e-4、optimizer=adam 不变，归因清晰。代码侧只做最小 family 原型接线，没有引入新 tunable，因此不存在 override/runner 静默回退风险。风险是当前 prototype 的 expert 数和 active_experts 仍是固定值，若首轮效果一般，不能立刻下结论否定 `lowrank + expert` 方向本身。","summary":"已实现并 smoke 通过新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` family，用最小 lowrank+expert 原型覆盖当前高优先级未验证结构槽位。建议下一轮以 r12(topk K=128 EF=1) 为参考，只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，先在约 0.56x total_cost 的低开销带验证该 family 是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
