y，不是动态字典。","本轮要回答的是三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
