research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0136.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，已满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。本轮只改一个主变量 NUM_CODES，把 codebook 容量下调到 32，回答一个问题：在保持主线 family 与 recipe 不变的前提下，是否能以更低的 code_router/codebook_matmul 选择成本和更低的 codebook_deploy 成本，维持接近当前 0.0581 的 FVU，从而形成更强的 LUTurbo 成本侧 Pareto 点。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0250.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"On the directly compatible `topk` line, increasing `K` from 96 to 160 should produce a materially better `<0.5x` Pareto point, likely around the low-0.18 FVU range at about 0.41x total_cost, while avoiding the recent `factorized_topk` pattern of modest quality gains paired with worse throughput.","summary":"Use `topk` as the next low-cost mainline probe, anchored to r242 and changing only `K` to 160. Final reconstruction formula remains `x_hat = Σ_{i in TopK(x)} α_i(x) b_i`, where all `b_i` come from one static vector library, so this family is `直接兼容` with the LUTurbo/Lottable `查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿` path. This is a strict single-variable step inside the target `<0.5x` region: estimated selection cost stays at the EF=1 topk baseline, deployment lookup rises with `K`, and combined cost should land near 0.41x, filling the gap between the existing 0.38x/0.1968 and 0.44x/0.1635 topk points. Recent `factorized_topk` rounds improved FVU only slightly while increasing runtime cost, so the cleaner frontier-building move is to continue the already monotone-improving topk K ladder.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This is intentionally conservative: it does not open a new family, and it relies on the existing topk trend rather than a new mechanism. The tradeoff is that it will not teach much about new structure, but that is acceptable here because the current priority is to strengthen the `<0.5x` Pareto frontier with a deployable, directly compatible point and to avoid recipes that slow training without a commensurate FVU gain.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Recent `factorized_topk` rounds remained far above the best low-cost topk points, and the wider scorer pass at r249 also reduced throughput to about 111k tok/s, so further factorized widening is currently a weak cost-quality bet.","The EF=1 `topk` K ladder has shown consistent FVU improvement from K=96 to K=128 to K=192 without any compatibility risk; an untested midpoint K=160 is the cleanest next `<0.5x` frontier probe."],"next_hypotheses":["If `topk` K=160 lands near the expected ~0.18 FVU at ~0.41x, test `K=176` next to refine the mid-right edge of the `<0.5x` frontier.","If `topk` K=160 underperforms the monotone trend, shift the next round to a different directly compatible low-cost selector family instead of continuing dense K sweeps.","If runtime regresses disproportionately at K=160, treat that as a system-side warning and prefer lower-cost frontier densification over larger-K topk pushes."],"reference_round":242}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0224.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"96"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r u_r + Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是静态 trunk 向量库、{b_i} 是静态 residual 向量库；在线侧只计算 trunk 系数 β_r 与 residual 稀疏系数 α_i，再执行 trunk 查表 + residual 查表 + 加权求和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。r223 已确认 `topk@EF1,K248` 的 recipe 轴继续向上推 LR 只带来更差 FVU 和明显更差吞吐，说明当前 <0.5x 最强 topk 锚点已基本饱和；同时 r221 说明直接压 `TRUNK_RANK` 会破坏 lowrank_factorized_residual 的 trunk 表达。基于 r210 这个高质量参考点，本轮严格只改一个 env 参数 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96`，保留 `K=64, EF=1, signum, LR=3e-3` 与完整 trunk 分支不变，用更短的 factorized scorer 链路替代默认较宽隐藏层，测试是否能把该 family 的 total_cost 从 0.69x 压到约 0.48x，同时尽量保留显著优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 在约 0.48x 成本下仍明显优于 `topk@0.48x` 的 FVU=0.1483，且训练吞吐没有像 r221 那样恶化，则下一轮相对本轮继续单变量下探到 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=64`，寻找更低成本拐点。","如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 FVU 明显退化到接近或差于同成本 topk，则说明该 family 的优势主要来自更宽 scorer 而非 trunk 本身；下一轮应关闭这条 scorer 压缩线，转向新的低成本 family。","如果该配置质量接近 r210 但系统代价明显更差，则保留其为解释性对照，不继续把该 family 作为 <0.5x 主战场。"],"notes_to_memory":["r223 给出明确负面信号：`topk@EF1,K248` 的向上 LR 分支已不值得继续，后续应把注意力从 topk recipe 清洗转回新低成本结构。","本地 `selection_cost_estimate()` 显示 `lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 combined_ratio 约为 0.48x，已进入当前重点搜索区间，而不需要再次牺牲 trunk。","与压 `TRUNK_RANK` 不同，压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 只缩短 factorized scorer 链路，保留 trunk 静态库的容量，更符合当前“降低选择成本但不破坏导出结构”的目标。"],"reference_round":210,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对有效参考轮 r210 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，family、K、EF、optimizer、LR 及其他结构参数全部不变。选择 96 而不是 128，是因为 128 只会把总成本压到约 0.50x 边界，仍不够明确进入当前主目标区；选择 96 而不是更激进的 64，则是为了先做最小但有效的 scorer 压缩，尽量保留 r210 已证明存在的质量优势。","summary":"相对 r210 的 `lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1` 做一次严格 param_only 低成本压缩，仅设置 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96`，验证保留完整 trunk 时，缩短 factorized scorer 链路能否把该 family 推入 `<0.5x` Pareto 主前沿。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0147.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"confirm_signal","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r145 表明把 signum 学习率从主线参考值 3.0e-3 小幅上调到 3.3e-3 后，FVU 从 0.058106 降到 0.057939，且总耗时未恶化；r146 的 policy_reject 说明不能把这一步包装成 clean baseline，本轮必须继续作为单变量 LR 问题处理。本轮只回答一个问题：相对于当前主线参考配方的 LR=3.0e-3，把 LR 改为 3.3e-3 的收益是否可重复成立，并且不会以更差的 tokens_per_sec、总耗时或 final_total_tokens 为代价。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 LR=3.3e-3 再次优于 3.0e-3，且运行代价基本不变，则可把 3.3e-3 视为新的 signum 主线锚点，后续再决定是否继续微调或转入 optimizer/成本轴。","若 LR=3.3e-3 回落到 3.0e-3 基线附近，则说明 r145 更可能是噪声收益，后续应关闭上探并保守回到 3.0e-3。","若 LR=3.3e-3 只带来极小收益但显著拖慢训练，则将其视为负面 recipe 信号，不再继续围绕更高 LR 上探。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍是当前兼容 frontier 上质量最强的可行主线，导出形式未变，继续属于扩展兼容。","r145 首次在 EF=2/K=128/signum 主线上得到 0.057939，因此当前最有价值的问题是确认这个 LR 信号是否可复现。","r146 的 policy_reject 表明必须把 3.3e-3 继续视为 LR 轴单变量问题，而不是以 clean baseline 名义提交。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 LR，family、EF、K、optimizer 与导出形式全部固定，不混入成本轴、loss 轴或新的结构变化。这样既符合当前推荐顺序，也避开了 r146 暴露出的 clean-baseline 包装问题。风险是再次运行 3.3e-3 可能只复现到接近 3.0e-3 的结果，因此评估时必须同时看完整曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，而不是只看最终 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕当前主线 family 推进，不开新 family；将 r145 的 3.3e-3 结果当作单变量 LR 信号而非新 baseline，保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum 不变，再运行一次 LR=3.3e-3，确认该小幅上调是否能稳定优于参考配方的 3.0e-3。","touched_files":[]}
